data.description: Stately 2 story ranch home with 7 bedrooms, 9 bathrooms plus an additional 420sqft detached guest house! The majesty of this unique home will captivate you the moment you enter the threshold of this estate and behold this picturesque property from a distant perspective. This is a 2-acre haven in the middle of which is a 2 story home replete with charming features – porches and balconies, roof turret, abundant windows and other exquisite details. Impeccable attention to detail is evident throughout.  The home celebrates warm natural wood accents in the doors, floors, window casements, paneling, fireplaces, crown molding and built-ins creating an atmosphere of rustic refinement. The heart of this home is the spacious eat-in kitchen complete with a grand island, 5 burner gas stove, and generously-sized pantry, as well as a separate formal dining space with stunning coffered wood ceiling. Exuding timeless character, there’s an incredible  classic sit-down wet bar with sink and ice maker. Elevating the indoor ambiance, soaring ceilings and oversized windows flood the interiors with an abundance of natural light, infusing the living spaces with a radiant warmth.  Welcoming you through double doors, the primary suite features a  fireplace, built-in window seat, 2 walk-in closets and an ensuite refuge with spa tub, double sinks, separate shower, bidet and a versatile adjoining room suitable for an exercise/weight/yoga room (or whatever your heart desires). There’s an additional upstairs guest space with a family room, bedroom and bathroom and accessible by an outside staircase. You’ll also find a lovely dedicated office space with built-ins galore in a unique wood paneled turreted ceiling. Outdoors you’ll find a magnificent backyard entertainer’s paradise with a covered kitchen/bar, a gazebo-covered spa, tennis courts with large covered area adjacent, lovely pool, barn with 2 horse stables, arena, and fully equipped guest cottage with grassy and treed landscaped expanses, front and back. While this compound exudes a sense of seclusion and tranquility reminiscent of a distant retreat, it remains conveniently connected. Despite feeling worlds awau from the city, it's under 20-minutes to the I5 freeway and just 10 minutes to Hwy. 14, seamlessly combining the best of both worlds.
